<section>
    <h3>Complexity</h3>

    <p>
        With the Curation Interface, the complexity of business logic in not
        due to chemistry rules (this is covered by PP/RDkit) but the nature of 
        complex one-to-many relation between unique molecule and its records 
        (occurences).
    </p>	

</section>

